metadata.name: DogeChex: Chex Doge
metadata.description:
The first drip is #1 in the collection of 10 total. This one-of-a-kind, hand-carved, gold-leaf encrusted NFT was forged in the USA by freemason blacksmiths atop the Blue-Ridge mountains while fending off a rabid pack of coyotes during a tornado just after a devastating measles outbreak nearly decimated the entire population of settlers living in the valley below. 

This edition of NFTs is nearly all that remains of the good people's noble efforts to survive the harsh conditions of pioneer life after a great & dreadful forest fire swept through and took all that was left of their humble village in the winter of '92. 

Own a piece of history in their honor today.
